Frameworks used

Testing
- Mocha npm install mocha --save,  create mocha.opts in test --reporter spec and --recursive. Mocha runs on all files with describe and outputs to the 'spec.
- Chai npm install chai --save-dev - this is the assertion module makes the syntax easier
- Zombie npm install zombie --save-dev

Setup
- Nodemon npm install nodemon --save

API
- Express npm install express --save
